				<td colspan="2"><span>One suggestion I could make on a tiny guild is make friends... Even if you don't group a lot like me (til recently), I have a great way to get help on epics... BARDS!  For the most part, uber bards in uber guilds love to help friendly lower level bards that know their class.  I have met several bards from here that play on my server and always like chatting with higher level bards.  That has gotten me several unsolicited offers to have them and their friends help me on my epic if needed.  You never know, they may also have a spare phinny spine in the bank that nobody needs =)
